be interesting as well.

00:01:08.030 --> 00:01:10.740
So I said, sure, come
talk to us about that.

00:01:10.740 --> 00:01:11.760
So he'll do that.

00:01:11.760 --> 00:01:14.330
I think he'll be taking
some questions at the end.

00:01:14.330 --> 00:01:16.820
We can talk about the book
a little bit then as well,

00:01:16.820 --> 00:01:18.570
