Two seconds of
data would fill up

00:45:59.810 --> 00:46:04.854
a CD, which was state of the art
optical storage in those days.

00:46:04.854 --> 00:46:06.770
And it's also the world's
biggest garbage can,

00:46:06.770 --> 00:46:08.990
because we threw this all out,
except for the occasional stuff

00:46:08.990 --> 00:46:09.842
that we didn't.

00:46:09.842 --> 00:46:11.330
So that was cool.

00:46:11.330 --> 00:46:12.030
That was cool.

