00:49:40.460 --> 00:49:44.210
a three-foot secondary, the
mount, and the drive system

00:49:44.210 --> 00:49:45.560
and everything for $50,000.

00:49:45.560 --> 00:49:47.590
A real bargain, so
we got this thing.

